{"tid":1729969,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[Myradio]《癲狗日報》攝記遭水炮車水柱射中須手術抽出瘀血","createTime":"2019-11-17T11:52:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T11:49:47.000Z","uid":219007,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"20aa015fa48f6010853e63fb64687a34c781263d","tid":1729969,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:52:54.000Z","msg":"《癲狗日報》攝記遭水炮車水柱射中須手術抽出瘀血<br />\n<br />\n一名《癲狗日報》的攝影記者下午在理工大學外圍期間，遭警方水炮車的水柱射中，記者頭部流血，當場休克，送院治理。《癲狗日報》總編輯梁錦祥發聲明表示，該名記者經診斷後，證實後腦骨折，並有腦部出血，須進行手術抽出瘀血。梁錦祥表示，記者在理工大學外圍進行正常採訪，在沒有任何示威活動範圍內，遭警方以水炮重力射擊，記者當時即使身穿保護裝備，頭部及腰部仍嚴重傷害，當場休克，隨身攝影器材盡毀，須由在場人士協助急救送院。《癲狗日報》表示，強烈譴責殘害新聞自由及傷害記者人身安全的行為，並保留追究法律及刑事責任的權利。"},{"pid":"a70de549a6346a69ce173faaeed534b1ec8cc5a5","tid":1729969,"uid":53037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:58:23.000Z","msg":"死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c50a27c229b77af13fda4a3d7fcc7bff7db8098f","tid":1729969,"uid":196758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T11:58:42.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b8bc06324d4a9e2073ac996bf803db0967c65a","tid":1729969,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:00:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n魔警死清光"},{"pid":"6a08ac2434c50cad1a074be2c6c53c79f9994bf1","tid":1729969,"uid":27112,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:00:36.000Z","msg":"希望唔好有後遺症"},{"pid":"c61d24f7ba55fa3085c040e7b51cc39de340db9b","tid":1729969,"uid":322549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T12:02:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/p